        <levelledPara>
          <title>Structural Safety</title>
          <para>
            WARNING: Do not exceed specified load limits. Structural overload can result 
            in permanent deformation or failure. Always use proper lifting equipment and 
            support stands when working on Center Body structure.
          </para>
        </levelledPara>
        
        <levelledPara>
          <title>Composite Material Safety</title>
          <para>
            CAUTION: Composite dust from drilling or cutting operations can cause 
            respiratory irritation. Use approved respiratory protection and dust collection 
            systems. Follow Material Safety Data Sheets for all composite materials.
          </para>
        </levelledPara>
